****************LOGIN TO HOMEPAGE :

1. make utils folder in lib
2. make a routes.dart file in it
3. replace in main.dart:
        "/login": (context) => LoginPage(), --> with --> MyRoutes.loginRoute: (context) => LoginPage(),
        and same with the homepage 
4. then use the onPress in the login button page and use navigator:
ElevatedButton(
                    child: Text("Login"),
                    style: TextButton.styleFrom(
                      minimumSize: Size(150, 40)
                    ),
                    onPressed: () {
                      Navigator.pushNamed(context, MyRoutes.homeRoute);
                    },
                  ),
